quote: In my experience, when you think you understand the Force, you realize just how little you know.
author: Ahsoka Tano
Obi-wan Kenobi
quote: It takes strength to resist the dark side. Only the weak embrace it.
Remember, concentrate on the moment. Feel, don’t think. Trust your instincts.
author: Qui-gon Jinn

quote: If all I do is try, that means I don’t truly believe I can succeed.
author: Kanan Jarrus
Yoda
quote: Fear is the path to the dark side…fear leads to anger…anger leads to hate…hate leads to suffering.

author: Yoda
quote: Luminous beings are we, not this crude matter.
Confronting fear is the destiny of a Jedi.
author: Luke Skywalker

quote: A Jedi uses the force for knowledge and defense, never for attack.
author: Yoda

quote: You must unlearn what you have learned…No! Try not. Do. Or do not. There is no try.
author: Yoda
Obi-wan Kenobi
quote: you’re going to find that many of the truths we cling to depend greatly on our own point of view.

author: Ezra Bridger
quote: There will be loss and sacrifice. But we can't back down just because we're afraid. That's when we need to stand the tallest…Stand up together. Because that's when we're strongest—as one.
Keep your concentration here and now, where it belongs.
author: Qui-gon Jinn

quote: If you define yourself by the power to take life, the desire to dominate, to possess…then you have nothing.
author: Obi-wan Kenobi
Qui-gon Jinn
quote: Always remember, your focus determines your reality.
